<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>coderyoMC API @API_VERSION@</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0f1116;
            --panel: #181b22;
            --accent: #4f9cff;
            --accent-2: #7ee787;
            --text: #e6edf3;
            --muted: #9aa4b2;
            --border: #2a2f3a;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .wrap { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
        header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
        h1 .accent { color: var(--accent); }
        .version {
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-2);
            background: rgba(126, 231, 135, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.15rem 0.7rem;
        }
        .tagline { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; max-width: 60ch; }
        .cards { display: grid; gap: 1rem; grid-template-columns: 1fr; margin-top: 1rem; }
        @media (min-width: 640px) { .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
        a.card {
            display: block;
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text);
            transition: border-color 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
        }
        a.card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        a.card h2 { margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
        a.card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; }
        footer { margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
        code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; color: var(--accent-2); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <header>
            <h1>coderyo<span class="accent">MC</span> API</h1>
            <span class="version">apiVersion @API_VERSION@</span>
            <p class="tagline">
                Public API Javadoc for <strong>coderyoMC</strong> &mdash; a paperweight-v2
                hard-fork of PaperMC targeting Minecraft @API_VERSION@ with regionized
                multithreading and an optional GPU compute backend.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="cards">
            <a class="card" href="apidocs/index.html">
                <h2>API Javadoc &rarr;</h2>
                <p>Browse the generated reference for the <code>coderyo-api</code> public surface.</p>
            </a>
            <a class="card" href="apidocs/overview-tree.html">
                <h2>Class Hierarchy &rarr;</h2>
                <p>The full type hierarchy across all documented packages.</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            Generated from <code>com.coderyo</code> sources atop PaperMC @API_VERSION@.
            Built with the standard JDK 25 Javadoc tool. Regenerates as the API grows
            (region API, compat hooks, ComputeBackend SPI).
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
